snippet.title: Memoir En Code: Reissue - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/467940/
Humble: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/memoir-en-code-reissue
itch.io: https://alexkalopsia.itch.io/memoir-en-code-reissue

Trailer Soundtrack: 
Aloor (B-side) by Jukio "Kozilek" Kallio
https://kozilek.bandcamp.com/track/aloor-b-side

Memoir En Code: Reissue is an autobiographical game album. Designed to be experienced similarly to a music album, this short experimental game explores different bits of the author's life as a series of interactive tracks.
